**Shows:** Realistic example of a process for Doxee Workplace

This is a realistic example of a productive process used by Doxee Workplace. It fetches customer data from a webservice, templates are selected, preliminary documents are created from the templates and customer data, those can be modified in two subsequent steps, PDFs are rendered from the preliminary documents, can be previewed, are uploaded to the repository and sent via email. The required resources are included in the folder of the process. Setting it up within Workplace requires specific knowledge about the application and the used human tasks. For detailed information regarding these topics, please consult the Doxee Workplace documentation.
